&lt;li&gt;Own architecture and design of electrical systems spanning Super Pressure flight avionics, distributed power, battery packs/BMS, solar charging, downstream DC/DC conversion, CAN/RS-485 networking, satellite communications, GPS/GNSS, pressure/temperature sensing, winch/motor control, cutter/termination circuits, and bus/interconnect boards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own power-budget and electrical-architecture trades for day/night mission profiles, battery/solar sizing, load shedding, comms blackouts, modular mission configurations, and fault-tolerant operation.&lt;/li&gt;
